affymetrix.calvin.parameter
Class ParameterNameValue

java.lang.Object
  affymetrix.calvin.parameter.ParameterNameValue
Direct Known Subclasses:
ParameterNameValueDefaultRequired
public class ParameterNameValue
extends java.lang.Object

A class to hold a parameter name/value/type. This class will convert several built-in types between the MIME string and their native types.
